### Fetch machine-readable Person profile
GET /llm/alex-example HTTP/1.1
Host: example.org
Accept: application/ld+json

###

# Expected response (200 OK)
# HTTP/1.1 200 OK
# Content-Type: application/ld+json
# Cache-Control: public, max-age=300
# ETag: "abc123def456"
# Vary: Accept, Accept-Language
# 
# {
#   "@context": "https://schema.org",
#   "@type": "ProfilePage",
#   ...
# }

### Example curl command
curl -H "Accept: application/ld+json" \
     -v \
     https://example.org/llm/alex-example

###

### Revalidation with If-None-Match (304 Not Modified)
GET /llm/alex-example HTTP/1.1
Host: example.org
Accept: application/ld+json
If-None-Match: "abc123def456"

###

# Expected response (304 Not Modified)
# HTTP/1.1 304 Not Modified
# Cache-Control: public, max-age=300
# ETag: "abc123def456"
# Vary: Accept, Accept-Language

### Example curl command for revalidation
curl -H "Accept: application/ld+json" \
     -H "If-None-Match: \"abc123def456\"" \
     -v \
     https://example.org/llm/alex-example

